{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"viewForAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view that requested the annotation view."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to display an annotation image instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method or have it return ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" for that annotation, then implement","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is an instance of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" (or equal to the map view’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property), return an instance of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or a subclass thereof)."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" to use for a given "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" object on your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L753"},"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"View representing an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" on screen."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"title":"MLNUserLocation","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"topic"}}}